name: Tommy Mommy
description: Street Cats of Vis is a project I founded on the island of Vis, in Croatia. Tommy Mommy is one of the cats living near the Tommy supermarket. We monitor the Tommy colony: all the cats are spayed or neutered and have regular food, water and shelter. If you'd like to support this project, you can make a donation at streetcatsofvis.com (mention HEN if you do!)
